#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<acronym>IO</acronym> Slaves enable &kde; applications to access remote "
#| "resources as easily as local resources (making them \"network transparent"
#| "\"). Remote resources (&eg; files) might be stored on <acronym>SMB</"
