#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:440
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Oxygen is the default theme of &kde; SC 4. Designed to bring 'a breath of "
#| "fresh air' to the desktop by removing the simplistic, cartoonish icons, "
#| "and replacing them with a clean theme and photo-realistic icons. Oxygen "
#| "uses a desaturated palette to avoid the icons becoming a distraction and "
